      "blocks": [
        {
          "uid": "bx576wqdn",
          "type": "meta"
        },
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Overview",
          "uid": "b5d13791r"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "In 2024, HDFC Bank signed PayZapp as a lead sponsor of IPL. The campaigns, mechanics, and offers were defined by the bank. What came to us was the brief — make it work inside the app.\nOur job was to take what was handed to us and build an experience around it. One that felt like the season, not just a banner.",
          "uid": "baej6r1mo"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bzrd47coj",
          "type": "spacer",
          "size": "md"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b7rhp1liv",
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "problem"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bno0ea8w2",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "The sponsorship guaranteed visibility. It didn't guarantee engagement. "
        },
        {
          "uid": "b7x6ecgtx",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Users seeing PayZapp on JioCinema would open the app to find a standard payments experience with no sense of the season. The gap between the sponsorship's promise and the in-app reality was the design problem."
        },
        {
          "uid": "b73l0j1k3",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Two campaigns were running through the season:"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bogmzdvde",
          "type": "image",
          "layout": "2-col",
          "src": "",
          "alt": "",
          "items": [
            {
              "src": "",
              "alt": "",
              "uid": "b5zeneolw"
            },
            {
              "src": "",
              "alt": "",
              "uid": "b9d00k2su"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "uid": "b0apxby0c"
    },
    {
      "id": "process",
      "label": "Process",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Process",
          "uid": "bfgmfy040"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "Campaigns and mechanics came to us as briefs — we weren't the authors of what users would be doing. We proposed the visual direction and designed the experience around the given logic.",
          "uid": "b1gomrpc4"
        },
        {
          "uid": "b0usnwyjn",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "That started with a surface audit: every screen we could touch, and what each one could carry. The proposal was an IPL event layer across the app — ambient enough that users felt the season before they even tapped into a campaign."
        }
      ],
      "uid": "bo565g0yo"
    },
