        {
          "uid": "biwd9ghub",
          "type": "feature-1",
          "headline": "Transaction Success",
          "body": "The circular tick became a bouncing ball. Pure delight post payments. Along side that, an animated bottom sheet confirmed your runs after every payment. Made the gamification feel immediate.",
