      "uid": "be27or06n"
    },
    {
      "id": "reflection",
      "label": "Reflection",
      "indexLabel": "Reflections",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "section-label",
          "label": "Reflection",
          "uid": "bchkbci1i"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<strong>Working within a brief is its own design skill.</strong> The campaigns were set. Making them feel like one coherent season required as much judgment as building from scratch.&nbsp;",
          "uid": "bzdv4w6wl"
        },
        {
          "uid": "bnukku1gm",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<strong>Delight at the right moment goes a long way.</strong> The scanner animations and the bouncing ball were small bets. They were the moments people actually noticed and talked about. Sometimes the highest-leverage design work is finding the right surface for a small moment."
        },
        {
          "uid": "be3svpjfw",
          "type": "text",
          "body": "This was a key visual design project I got to be a part of with an amazing team,&nbsp;<a class=\"cs-inline-link\" data-pill-label=\"Checkout Ishant's work\" data-pill-image=\"cs-asset:zapp-account:1782587619171:bxrgjdpsm\" data-href=\"https://ishantp.com/\" href=\"https://ishantp.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ishant</a>&nbsp;leading the motion design along with <strong>Vibhore</strong> on leading the direction of this project.",
          "spaceBefore": 0
        },
        {
          "uid": "bccyu4tfz",
          "type": "eyebrow-heading",
          "eyebrow": "",
          "headline": "💌 Get in touch for more details."
        }
      ],
      "uid": "bm1pbxtjz"
    }
  ],
